data.description: 14 MONTH HOME WARRANTY WITH ACCEPTED OFFER PRIOR TO 2/15/2024! Beautiful 4 bedroom/2 bathroom home in desirable Bemiss Landing! Situated on a large corner lot, this home offers a functional split floor plan. Step into the spacious great room with tray ceilings, wood accents, beautiful crown moulding, and an electric fireplace. Great room is open to the kitchen and dining rooms- perfect for entertaining. Kitchen includes custom cabinetry with tons of storage and counter space, stainless steel appliances (new refrigerator and dishwasher), stone backsplash, island with storage, and pantry. Primary suite includes three closets, dual vanities, soaking tub, and walk-in tiled shower with glass door. Easy to maintain LVP in all main areas and one guest bedroom, carpet in the other bedrooms, and tile in the kitchen/laundry/bathrooms. Front guest bedroom has beautiful vaulted ceilings and would be ideal for a home office, workout room, or flex space. Granite countertops throughout! The screened in patio and new pergola are the perfect place to relax. New privacy fence just installed on 3 sides of the backyard- additional fenced area within yard is the perfect area for pets. Solar panels provide a low monthly electric bill. 2 car garage, security camera system, sprinkler system, shed, and easy to maintain vinyl siding. Only a short walk to the community pool! Zoned for Lowndes County Schools. Convenient to Publix, Aldi, SGMC, Freedom Park, shopping, and restaurants. Eligible for VA loan assumption @ 2.25% interest rate and approximately 85K due at closing.
